Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.97,0:02:04.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第八幕\N布洛涅之夜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.48,0:02:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.66,0:02:26.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔贝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.25,0:02:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然进来做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.81,0:02:30.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.14,0:02:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我怎么叫你都不回答
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.89,0:02:36.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香榭丽舍的客人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.53,0:02:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.65,0:02:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说今日不想见您
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.47,0:02:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么口信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.13,0:02:46.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 没什么特别的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.82,0:02:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.61,0:02:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.46,0:02:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,望能赏光参观新别墅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.87,0:02:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邀请您参加晚会的请贴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.55,0:02:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请务必与家人同往
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.04,0:02:58.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荣幸之至
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.81,0:02:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.07,0:03:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在奥特伊的森林
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.07,0:04:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Banner;12;0;90,{\a6}{\fs20}Auteuil：巴黎西部市郊的一个区，莫里哀等作家喜爱居住的地方。周围是布洛涅（Boulogne）森林。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.20,0:03:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么荒凉的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.18,0:03:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 这是伯爵的个人意愿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.45,0:03:27.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里…似乎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.70,0:03:30.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前是属于维尔福先生的别墅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.85,0:03:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直是废墟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.03,0:03:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的女主人在时 这里非常华丽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.63,0:03:41.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是瓦朗蒂娜的亲生母亲？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.64,0:03:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时还是年轻貌美的女士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.41,0:04:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.32,0:04:10.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将军阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.71,0:04:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承蒙邀请
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.18,0:04:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.37,0:04:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 是维尔福夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.07,0:04:26.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是外子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.07,0:04:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是首席检察官大人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.37,0:04:35.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说内人与犬子承蒙关照
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.15,0:04:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得您赏光亲临 实在蓬荜生辉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.61,0:04:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座别墅用来招待客人还稍显冷清
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.96,0:04:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里 不知为何我特别喜欢清静
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.78,0:05:00.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 如今代表巴黎的三位绅士都到齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.39,0:05:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金融王唐格拉尔氏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.93,0:05:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掌揽军队实权的莫尔塞夫将军
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.66,0:05:09.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有司掌法律的您
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.78,0:05:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今日招待各位参加这个简陋的聚会不为别桩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.88,0:05:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我向大家坦白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.27,0:05:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅者是不安之人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.82,0:05:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,望能和三位建立友情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.27,0:05:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将军阁下是否渴望大统领的地位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.40,0:05:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您从何处听闻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.59,0:05:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也请让我略尽绵薄之力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.94,0:05:48.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔贝 你先离席一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.40,0:05:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.51,0:05:52.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人之间有话要谈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.04,0:05:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.62,0:05:57.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔贝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.26,0:06:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 呆坐着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.99,0:06:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你脸色不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.26,0:06:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我没事 母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.04,0:06:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硬拉你过来 很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.05,0:06:31.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵…是不是在避开我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.34,0:06:33.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.93,0:06:35.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在维尔福先生家看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.70,0:06:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…伯爵和夫人有染
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.24,0:06:43.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.41,0:06:49.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候伯爵发现了我在偷窥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.87,0:06:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像…是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.88,0:06:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.17,0:06:56.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真差劲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.18,0:07:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵也有不为人知的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.95,0:07:05.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也是一个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.23,0:07:10.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你不是为了马克西米利安的事而去的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.73,0:07:14.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是另外一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.90,0:07:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.15,0:07:23.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能与二位相伴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.42,0:07:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.49,0:07:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去吹吹夜风
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.12,0:07:30.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 在下…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.40,0:07:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底干了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.14,0:07:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.58,0:07:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在…在…在下是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.80,0:07:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马克西米利安·莫雷尔大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.19,0:07:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是位杰出的军人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.28,0:07:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.38,0:07:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下猎犬座γ方面军陆军上尉 马克西米利安·莫雷尔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.39,0:07:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本家在马赛从事贸易 在下…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.12,0:08:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.08,0:08:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 在下和令媛…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.82,0:08:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您从事着保卫国家的高尚工作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.48,0:08:11.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此我对表示敬意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.82,0:08:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但您只是一介平民
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.59,0:08:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而小女已有未婚夫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.57,0:08:20.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此 望您谅解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.65,0:08:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真无礼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.68,0:08:29.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是越洋而来的马赛风味
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.72,0:08:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求婚怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.88,0:08:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没戏了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.18,0:08:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…她对你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.10,0:08:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在说什么悄悄话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.02,0:08:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博尚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.91,0:08:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然突然对首席检察官按下快门
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.06,0:08:55.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真够胆大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.45,0:08:59.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到嚣张的家伙就叛逆心理作祟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.96,0:09:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 青春的烦恼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.54,0:09:06.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 这世上一个二个都为情所困
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.38,0:09:12.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 以前那两人也传过绯闻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.17,0:09:15.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首席检察官和欧仁妮的母亲？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.97,0:09:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不情之请 实在抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.42,0:09:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 请别介意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.11,0:09:25.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上钢琴课也花了不少钱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.96,0:09:28.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就得在这种时候露两手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.56,0:09:39.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请听我说两句
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.41,0:09:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想向您道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.06,0:09:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时我…未考虑您的想法就出言不逊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.71,0:09:54.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦朗蒂娜怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.33,0:09:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.70,0:10:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦事都丢给你了 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.92,0:10:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦朗蒂娜喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.22,0:10:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.41,0:10:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.21,0:10:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.63,0:10:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧仁妮那家伙弹得不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.35,0:10:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要被她骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.65,0:10:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那会儿跟她聊过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.95,0:10:30.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正又是我说坏话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.99,0:10:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.28,0:10:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么呀 告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.40,0:10:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.01,0:10:43.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今还来找我干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.59,0:10:44.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.93,0:10:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被看见怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:49.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我在这里…把那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.65,0:11:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太美妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.70,0:11:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音乐就如您的天职
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.31,0:11:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天职吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.77,0:11:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵认识很多有才能的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.32,0:11:32.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢您出色的演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.31,0:11:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美丽的人儿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.92,0:11:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.90,0:11:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为展示年轻人们的才华横溢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.54,0:11:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,容我再引荐一位年轻人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.50,0:11:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安德烈亚·卡瓦尔坎蒂侯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.45,0:11:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个家族还有继承人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.43,0:12:03.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的父亲是我的旧友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.08,0:12:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若大家能像待我一样待他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.04,0:12:08.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便不胜荣幸了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.89,0:12:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是刚继承亡父领地的后生晚辈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.08,0:12:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.89,0:12:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看他的胸饰 看样子值500万
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.02,0:12:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.45,0:12:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵的新宠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.90,0:12:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.83,0:12:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能非常有才华哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.75,0:12:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 抱歉打断各位畅谈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.15,0:12:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能承蒙稍微侧目一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.86,0:12:44.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我买下这座别墅是为了远离城市喧嚣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.26,0:12:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过清静离群的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.00,0:12:50.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但说来也奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.69,0:12:57.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际来到这里的我迷上了这幢古宅的某种气氛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.27,0:13:01.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.39,0:13:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该如何形容呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.96,0:13:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.66,0:13:13.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是…诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.96,0:13:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不禁去想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.72,0:13:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从前这座别墅里人们过着怎样的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.74,0:13:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是隐藏了怎样不为人知的悲剧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.07,0:13:34.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次想起 我都充满着无以言表的喜悦和平稳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.92,0:13:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.48,0:13:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.10,0:13:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无聊 说什么诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.81,0:13:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,检察官大人察觉不到这座宅子里阴郁邪恶的气氛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.18,0:13:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是首席检察官
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.77,0:14:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那么由您亲自来确认一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.51,0:14:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实在这座宅子里只留有一间未使用的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.21,0:14:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.32,0:14:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那房间被认为是这邪恶气氛弥漫的核心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.53,0:14:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荒谬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.88,0:14:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.70,0:14:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.90,0:14:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了算了 不要这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.67,0:14:36.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚就遵从一下主人的意愿嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.46,0:14:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.61,0:14:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起来参观一下这间邪恶的房间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.47,0:14:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.34,0:14:48.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去的话 也无甚兴味
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.18,0:14:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔贝先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.68,0:14:52.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.76,0:14:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗朗兹先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.59,0:14:55.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有欧仁妮小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.63,0:14:57.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.25,0:15:01.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分成三组去寻找那间房 如何
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.57,0:15:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让三个年轻人先行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.62,0:15:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗宅邸至深之处
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.06,0:15:15.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将赠予平安到达的人一份薄礼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.00,0:15:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.29,0:15:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 非常有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.36,0:15:23.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.11,0:15:27.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔贝先生 拜托您了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.35,0:15:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.11,0:15:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久违了 侯爵夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.80,0:15:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您气色不错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.67,0:15:45.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请认真一点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.57,0:15:48.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先发方能制人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.70,0:15:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺带一问 侯爵出身何处？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.29,0:15:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我来自银河东方的远方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.54,0:15:59.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是一片非常美丽的行星群
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.71,0:16:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中某颗星上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.15,0:16:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一种吸取矿石菁华 孕育宝石之卵的鸟类
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.32,0:16:10.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,50年1次为繁殖而筑巢…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.27,0:16:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于能和您单独交谈了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.84,0:16:24.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失陪一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.64,0:16:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵 我想和您谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.20,0:16:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事 莫尔塞夫夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.80,0:16:51.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请叫我梅尔塞苔丝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.80,0:16:55.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪恶气氛的核心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.42,0:16:58.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,核心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.56,0:17:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.14,0:17:09.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您为何对马赛如此介怀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.75,0:17:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此话怎讲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.28,0:17:15.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚的菜肴也安排了马赛口味
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.59,0:17:18.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您不满意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.64,0:17:24.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 只是看到您就想起以前认识的某人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.76,0:17:31.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长久以来 我都只为再见他一面而活
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.39,0:17:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在不知为何却感到恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.21,0:17:43.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.06,0:17:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您不是孤独一人 绝不是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.79,0:17:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人一直想念着您
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.48,0:17:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要忘了那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.57,0:18:05.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是亡父给我的护身符
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.47,0:18:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望您能收下它
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.06,0:18:13.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到尽头了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.73,0:18:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,适可而止吧 阿尔贝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.37,0:18:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人也累了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.89,0:18:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.07,0:18:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维尔福先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.03,0:18:22.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面有门
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.22,0:18:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.25,0:18:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.41,0:18:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是第一名
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.31,0:18:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否感到愉快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.96,0:19:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对这座别墅奇异的气氛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.15,0:19:06.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这宅邸的主人看来不知何为待客之道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.09,0:19:11.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔贝先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.20,0:19:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请帮我一个小忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.40,0:19:15.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.53,0:19:21.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您如此帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.52,0:19:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.48,0:19:27.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.49,0:19:30.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.07,0:19:33.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.73,0:19:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看见了 在维尔福先生家的温室
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.31,0:19:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思 您看见了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.74,0:19:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人太热情了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.40,0:19:53.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为您一定非常生气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.78,0:19:55.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.10,0:20:05.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 应该由我说对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.46,0:20:09.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也无法与您畅谈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.07,0:20:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我在远方宇宙得了一种病
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.97,0:20:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时会不见任何人来修养
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.12,0:20:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.10,0:20:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.86,0:20:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔会感到麻痹而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.27,0:20:40.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔贝 这是只属于你和我的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.98,0:20:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只属于你和我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.80,0:20:50.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 我会保密的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.88,0:20:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 拿着这个盒子出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.47,0:20:58.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…那孩子出生的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.36,0:21:04.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子…是那孩子把我们引来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.53,0:21:05.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要慌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.18,0:21:08.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是17年前的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.25,0:21:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个声音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.58,0:21:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你们
